---
title: SuperQuick Cheesy Italian Turkey Wraps with Mozzarella and Peppers
description: Inspired by Mexican taquitos, this dish features crisped-up wraps stuffed with mozzarella cheese, turkey and peppers. You'll love the fusion of rich Italian flavours with the crunch of a tostada—perfect for dipping into the marinara sauce served on the side!

